# 🦊 Pelt & Powder Portfolio Website

This is the official portfolio website for **SolarisGooFox**.

It is a dark neon furry-themed portfolio website designed for sharing on:

- DeviantArt
- FurAffinity
- YouTube
- Other art communities

The website includes:

✅ Dark neon furry theme  
✅ Animated glowing buttons  
✅ Custom banner background  
✅ Full image gallery with zoom pop-up modal  
✅ Commission pricing page  
✅ Terms of Service page  
✅ FAQ page  
✅ Contact page with email form  
✅ Age-gate NSFW toggle system  
✅ Search + filter gallery system  
✅ Light/Dark theme switcher (optional)

---

# 🌐 Live Website

Once hosted, the site will be available here:

**https://pelt-powder.github.io**

